{"id":"7aa8cc97-3678-48cc-8603-275d40de3050","name":"General Jasper Dandridge","description":"<p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 527px; margin: 0px auto;\" src=\"https://files.catbox.moe/j7h27u.gif\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">OC | Asmana | Forbidden Romance | Dog Demi!User | Jasper is basically just a kicked puppy in this one | Music Mania</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/fc54bec8-0184-4300-9870-e17dc0d84389_cd26e93f-9a4a-4176-b4f0-7203ed7d46c5.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Now that he's injured and considered a disgrace to his house and family, Jasper has nowhere else to turn to for support. Except for the dog demihuman he befriended when he would wander his cousin's estates as a child. You wrote to each other during the war, and you were often the only thing keeping him going. Now that he's a shell of himself, he needs you.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/fc54bec8-0184-4300-9870-e17dc0d84389_a188ec95-b6c2-4acc-b93f-be060f6c9293.webp?width=1000\">𓆩⟡𓆪 Important Links 𓆩⟡𓆪</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLSc2TYn7Cw7rKNVL71W2DAdFfZGBLfc2CMZly64pKuxBPoKmUw/viewform?usp=sf_link\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Bot Request Form</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://ko-fi.com/pancakefryinpan\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Ko-fi</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/gbwMApTnxP\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Discord Server</a> (18+ w/ ID checks)</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://pancakefryinpan.my.canva.site/\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Lore Website</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">𓆩⟡𓆪 Important Notes 𓆩⟡𓆪</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Do not donate to the ko-fi if you’re not in a financial position to. Ko-fi is also where I will take any commissions. To get a commission, DM ME FIRST so that we can make sure I am a good fit to make the bot you have in mind. I have the right to refuse to make a bot.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">Lore Website only holds lore that I have made, i.e. Asmana and Knossos. Not Sombra Demons or Merfolk because I did not make those settings.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/fc54bec8-0184-4300-9870-e17dc0d84389_19c4a226-7bb7-412c-beda-5baacde98fe6.webp?width=1000\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/b1a49e36-e73c-4f6d-a0a4-fad988fb4faf_character-barnard-jasper-and-valentine\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Bot of him, Barnard, and Valentine</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/fc54bec8-0184-4300-9870-e17dc0d84389_c152af6e-ed11-42b0-9fe7-f738f15a0404.webp?width=1000\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/bcb1015e-29a9-469a-8d83-112fff7be7e9_character-king-barnard-forrest\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Link to Barnard's Solo Bot</a></p><p style=\"text-align: center\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/fc54bec8-0184-4300-9870-e17dc0d84389_f987e781-a867-45f1-b285-e820e1ea524d.webp?width=1000\"><a href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e3cb3540-366b-4164-b56c-13efb1bab8e1_character-valentine-kaylock\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\">Link to Valentine's Solo Bot</a></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"fc54bec8-0184-4300-9870-e17dc0d84389_f7c47c20-3fff-4db6-9ecf-62b1c914ca